## Usage

To use a viridis palette in your plot, include `scale_*_viridis()` in your ggplot2 call:



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
mpg |>  
  ggplot(aes(x = displ, y = cty, color = hwy)) +
    geom_point() +
    scale_color_viridis(option = "A")
```
:::
